name: Ocean Skies
description: This is a fully kitted luxurious cabin that is beautifully furnished and decorated to the theme of our tranquil ocean surrounds. The cabin has the following facilities: Aircon, a kitchenette with a fridge, a small stove, a microwave and a coffee station with a lavish seating area. This cabin has an outdoor shower that will still leave you feeling like you are a part of the outdoors. There is nothing more relaxing than having a shower whilst staring at the moon, hearing the waves crashing in the background. Over and above this, if you feel like a calm night in there is a braai on the front patio of the cabin that allows you to take in the gorgeous ocean and surroundings.
